<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Buckle up, because weŌĆÖre about to drag this concept kicking and screaming into the real world, roast its pretentious balls off, and see what actually <em>works</em> when you stop circle-jerking in LaTeX and start shipping.</p>
