where <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>Ō¬»</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">  \preceq  </annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.7719em; vertical-align: -0.136em;"></span><span class="mrel">Ō¬»</span></span></span></span> denotes prefix order. This is the natural setting for append-only histories.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">\begin{definition}[Extension-Monotone Admissibility]
A language <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">L</mi><mo>ŌŖå</mo><mi mathvariant="script">H</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">  \mathcal{L} \subseteq \mathcal{H}  </annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.8193em; vertical-align: -0.136em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal">L</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">ŌŖå</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right: 0.00965em;">H</span></span></span></span> is extension-monotone if for every history <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>H</mi><mo>Ōłł</mo><mi mathvariant="script">L</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">  H \in \mathcal{L}  </annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.7224em; vertical-align: -0.0391em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.08125em;">H</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">Ōłł</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal">L</span></span></span></span> the admissible continuation set
